The Dave Mathews Band is one of the few bands out there that I believe still make music becuase they like to make music, not for the money.  I admit it has been a while since I have been to a concert so I may be a bit out of date on things.  But when I went to a DMB concert, I was amazed at the number of recorders I saw.  DMB is one of the few bands that allow people to record their music at their concerts, which gave me a greater respect for them.<br>
